## ðŸ”§ CLI Tools

```bash
# Create new project
tachyon new my-api

# Generate module
tachyon generate service users --crud

# Code quality
tachyon lint all
```

ðŸ‘‰ [Full CLI documentation](./docs/12-cli.md)

