## ðŸ§ª Testing

```python
from tachyon_api.testing import TachyonTestClient

def test_hello():
    client = TachyonTestClient(app)
    response = client.get("/")
    assert response.status_code == 200
```

```bash
pytest tests/ -v
```

ðŸ‘‰ [Full Testing documentation](./docs/11-testing.md)

