## ðŸ“Š Why Tachyon?

| Feature | Tachyon | FastAPI |
|---------|---------|---------|
| **Serialization** | msgspec + orjson | pydantic |
| **Performance** | âš¡âš¡âš¡ Ultra-fast | âš¡ Fast |
| **Bundle Size** | Minimal | Larger |
| **Learning Curve** | Easy (FastAPI-like) | Easy |
| **Type Safety** | Full | Full |

